title: Uber and Lyft gear up for last leg of their IPO race
text: The race to the IPOs for Lyft and Uber. With CNBC's Melissa Lee and the Fast Money traders, Steve Grasso, Brian Kelly, Steve Chiavarone and Guy Adami.

title: Neiman Marcus Customers Deserve Physical Presence in New York, CEO Says
text: Geoffroy Van Raemdonck, chief executive officer at Neiman Marcus Group, discusses the opening of the brand's first store at Hudson Yards and serving the company's customer base in New York. He speaks with Blomberg's Emma Chandra.
